%% helios_v3 数据流图（dataflow.mmd）
%% v3 单 tick 完整数据流（含 5 层 Markov blanket）
%% 完成时间：2026-06-22 19:37+

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Ext as External<br/>小黑 / Channel
    participant L1 as Layer 1<br/>Boundary Owner
    participant L2 as Layer 2<br/>Active Inference
    participant L3 as Layer 3<br/>Self-Model
    participant L4 as Layer 4<br/>Reflection
    participant L5 as Layer 5<br/>Evolution + Governance
    participant LLM as LLM-as-PFC<br/>3 层

    %% ========== Tick 开始 ==========
    Ext->>L1: tick_n 开始<br/>外部 stimulus
    activate L1

    %% ========== Layer 1 Boundary ==========
    L1->>L1: check_signal<br/>验证 conditional separation
    L1->>L2: 合法 signal 进入 Layer 2
    deactivate L1
    activate L2

    %% ========== Layer 2 Active Inference ==========
    L2->>L2: SensoryIngress (02)<br/>+ generative model
    L2->>L2: RapidSalienceAppraisal (03)<br/>5-dim × generative model
    L2->>L2: Neuromodulator (04)<br/>9-dim hormone dual-timescale
    L2->>L2: InteroceptiveFeeling (05)<br/>Seth 2012 interoceptive

    Note over L2: Active Inference Owner<br/>5 层 hierarchical generative model<br/>+ variational free energy

    L2->>L2: variational_free_energy<br/>compute + minimize

    L2->>L3: 推算 active inference signal
    deactivate L2
    activate L3

    %% ========== Layer 3 Self-Model ==========
    L3->>L3: self_model_owner.observe_tick
    L3->>L3: 8 维 PTS update<br/>(bodily, experiential, affective,<br/>intersubjective, cognitive,<br/>narrative, ecological, normative)

    Note over L3: 8 sub-owners:<br/>Agency + Egocentric + ToM<br/>+ Autobiographical + Material + Culture

    L3->>L3: Rochat level check<br/>推进 Level 1 → 5

    L3->>L4: 当前 8 维 PTS matrix
    deactivate L3
    activate L4

    %% ========== Layer 4 Reflection ==========
    L4->>L4: reflection_owner.reflect<br/>4 trigger

    alt POST_TICK trigger
        L4->>LLM: LLM reasoning<br/>反思本 tick
    else RESTING_STATE trigger
        L4->>LLM: LLM DMN-like<br/>深度反思
    else HIGH_UNCERTAINTY trigger
        L4->>LLM: LLM uncertainty<br/>reduction planning
    else USER_INVOKED trigger
        L4->>LLM: LLM user-invoked<br/>reflection
    end

    LLM-->>L4: insight + reasoning

    L4->>L3: 反思更新 8 维 PTS<br/>（向 self_model_owner 反馈）

    L4->>L5: reflection record<br/>+ 当前状态
    deactivate L4
    activate L5

    %% ========== Layer 5 Evolution ==========
    L5->>L5: governance_owner.enforce_gate<br/>4 个 gate

    Note over L5: 4 类 evolution:<br/>content / parameter / strategy / code<br/>每个都有严格 gate

    L5->>L5: fitness_gate verify<br/>(testing + evaluation +<br/>observability + audit)

    alt fitness gate 通过
        L5->>L5: evolution apply<br/>(content / parameter /<br/>strategy / code evolution)
    else fitness gate 拒绝
        L5->>L5: 拒绝 + 审计
    end

    L5-->>L1: evolution done<br/>+ audit log
    deactivate L5

    %% ========== LLM-as-PFC 3 层 ==========
    Note over LLM: LLM-as-PFC 3 层:<br/>Layer A: System Prompt (永久身份)<br/>Layer B: CSO (持续状态)<br/>Layer C: Reflection (反思)

    L3->>LLM: 8 维 PTS matrix + Rochat level
    L4->>LLM: reflection trigger + context
    LLM->>LLM: System Prompt + CSO + Reflection<br/>3 层组装
    LLM-->>L1: Action / Output
    activate L1

    %% ========== Action 输出 ==========
    L1->>L1: check_action<br/>验证 action 通过 Markov blanket
    L1->>Ext: 输出到 channel
    deactivate L1

    %% ========== Tick 结束 ==========
    Note over L1, L5: tick_n 结束<br/>下一 tick tick_n+1 开始